<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.10.7">
<l>kaṉṟu koṇṭuvi ḷaṅkaṉi yeṟin tuvā niraikkaḻi veṉṟumā maḻai</l>
<l>niṉṟu kāttukan tāṉnila māmakaṭ kiṉiyāṉ</l>
<l>kuṉṟiṉ mullaiyiṉ vācamuṅ kuḷir malli kaimaṇa mumaḷain tiḷan</l>
<l>teṉṟal vantula vuntiruk kōṭṭiyū rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who was content, standing guarding against the great torrent</l>
<l rend="indent">that was the destruction of the cattle herd,</l>
<l>Having taken a calf and thrown [it] for woodapples,</l>
<l rend="indent">the sweet[heart] of great lady earth,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr where the soft southern breeze</l>
<l rend="indent">comes [and] wanders,</l>
<l>Blending the fragrance of hill jasmine with the scent of cooling jasmine.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
